{"tid":1353724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 新民黨晤陳茂波 倡預算案全民派錢8000元","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:24:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":291,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"368397598df7ac52662f5812fe10d87bfc743059","tid":1353724,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"新民黨主動約見財政司司長陳茂波，就明年發表的《財政預算案》提出建議。新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示，建議政府向18歲或以上永久居民一筆過派發8000元現金津貼、向初生嬰兒家庭派發一筆過2萬元資助、豁免商業車輛一年驗車費，以及部分中小企一年牌照費等。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀說，由於中美貿易戰持續，加上近期社會氣氛緊張，抗爭不斷，直接影響基層市民和商戶，她認為，全民派錢定能安撫部份市民。不過，她強調，相關措施不可能直接紓緩到目前緊張的社會氣氛，因為就算落實，最快都要下年。被指早半年主動約見財爺並為預算案提建議是為年尾的區議會選舉鋪路，葉劉淑儀不認同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1050595/即時-香港-新民黨晤陳茂波-倡預算案全民派錢8000元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1050595%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%96%B0%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E6%99%A4%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-%E5%80%A1%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A28000%E5%85%83&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUilQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=92565c9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1050595%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%96%B0%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E6%99%A4%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2-%E5%80%A1%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A28000%E5%85%83&h=b29128a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1050595/即時-香港-新民黨晤陳茂波-倡預算案全民派錢8000元</a>"},{"pid":"7dd646b45da02b79fe879385ec184dc0a97aa3a5","tid":1353724,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b3ada63ba13fb06400166a0bab7a26f55ff1f7","tid":1353724,"uid":141176,"like":234,"dislike":0,"score":234,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"我4000都未收到<img src=